# Changelog
## [0.0.2] - 2024-04-26
### Added
- Implemented frontend React application structure
- Created user authentication components (Login and Register)
- Added Dashboard component for authenticated users
- Connected frontend to backend API endpoints
- Implemented JWT token-based authentication flow
- Added protected routes that require authentication
- Configured Nginx to serve the React application and proxy API requests
- Added responsive styling for authentication forms
- Created form validation for user registration and login